            </did>
            <scopecontent id="aspace_947056f93ca7503c2d74c873e2c6bee5">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The collection contains only correspondence from 1894 to 1899.  The files contain maijnly letters received, althiough there is an occasional draft of a letter by Etheridge. ASmong his corresoppndents are a number of women patients who were operated on by Etheridge. Also in the collection, but not in this series, are carbons of typed correspondence sent by Etheridge.</p>
               <p>The correspondence was housed in two boxes of Amberg's Popular Letter File sold by Amberg File &amp; Index Co., Chicago. Many of the leters were not acurately filed under the proper letter in the index.</p>
            </scopecontent>
